---
By: Dalai Lama
Source:
  URL: https://twitter.com/DalaiLama/status/992335581240799232
  Locus:
    Date: 4 May 2018
---
Scientists warn that constant fear and anger are bad for our health, while
being compassionate and warm-hearted contributes to our physical and mental
well-being, Therefore, just as we observe physical hygiene to stay well,
we need to cultivate a kind of emotional hygiene too.
